snippet.title: Ys X: Nordics - Release Date Announcement Trailer (Nintendo Switch, PS4, PS5, PC)
snippet.description:
Explore uncharted islands, engage in fast-paced action combat, and experience the high seas adventures of unlikely allies Adol and Karja in Ys X: Nordics, coming to Nintendo Switch, PS4, PS5, and PC on October 25, 2024!

Preorder now @ https://nisamerica.com/ys-x/

#YsX #YsXNordics
